{extends file="layout.html"}
{block name="title"}服装色彩数据分析_服装流行色推荐_色彩流行趋势-POP服装趋势网{/block}
{block name=keywords}服装色彩数据分析,服装流行色,服装色彩推荐,服装色彩流行趋势{/block}
{block name=description}POP服装趋势网智能+色彩数据栏目为服装企业和设计师提供服装流行色彩全方位分析、色彩走势情况预测、未来色彩流行推荐等，从各个方向为设计师提供全面及时的色彩数据解读。{/block}

{block name="selfcss"}
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="{STATIC_URL2}/global/css/color-data.css?{STATIC_CHANGE_TIME}">
{/block}

{block name="main"}
<div class="viewport">
    <input class="params" type="hidden" data-params="{$params}">
    <!-- 头图 -->
    <div class="banner">
        <div></div>
    </div>
    <!-- 导航选项 -->
    <div class="nav clearfix">
        <div class="nav-content w1500">
            <div class="fl">
                <ul class="nav-sex clearfix js-nav-sex">
                    {foreach $genders as $item}
                    <li {if intval($paramsArr['gen'])==$item['id']}class="active"{/if}><i></i><a href="{$item.link}">{$item.name}</a></li>
                    {/foreach}
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="fr">
                <div class="nav-week js-nav-week">
                    <span class="js-nav-week-name">{$selected_region_name}</span><i></i>
                    <ul class="nav-week-options">
                        {foreach $regions as $item}
                        <li {if intval($paramsArr['reg'])==$item['id']}class="active"{/if}><a href="{$item.link}">{$item.name}</a></li>
                        {/foreach}
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- 主体内容 -->
    <div class="viewport-content">
        <!-- 引导 -->
        <div class="guide-btn-box w1500">
            <div class="guide js-guide">
                <i></i>
                <span>新手小课堂</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 数据分析 -->
        <div class="section w1500 data-analysis js-analysis loading">
            <!-- 头部 -->
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="fl title">色彩单品组合占比分析</div>
                <div class="fr">
                    <div class="season season-box">
                        <ul class="season clearfix js-analysis-season">
                            {foreach $showYearSeason as $key=>$item}
                            <li {if $key==0}class="active"{/if} data-key='season' data-id="{$item.season_id}">{$item.year}{$item.season}</li>
                            {/foreach}
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="pager js-season-pager">
                        <i class="l disabled"></i>
                        <i class="r"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 图表 -->
            <div class="section-chart">
                <div class="crumbs">
                    <div class="light-tips">
                        <i class="light"></i>
                        <div class="light-tips-content">
                            <i class="arrow"></i>
                            <ul>
                                <li>展示当前季节下发布会整体的单品、颜色等数据情况；</li>
                                <li>点击单品组装图可以查看单品下品类的数量；</li>
                                <li>点击右边色环，可查看该色系下所有颜色，并可以查看单品在该颜色分布情况。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="crumbs-content js-crumbs-analysis">
                        <div><span>数据分析</span></div>
                        <div><i></i><span>总览</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="loading hide"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="section-chart-content clearfix">
                    <div class="fl">
                        <div class="chart-box js-chart-bar-analysis"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="fr">
                        <div class="chart-box js-chart-pie-analysis"></div>
                        <div class="color-title js-color-title">
                            <div><i class="l"></i><span>0%</span>有色系</div>
                            <div><i class="r"></i><span>0%</span>无色系</div>
                            <span>色系</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 数据解读 -->
            <div class="section-chart-interpreta">
                <img class="title" src="{STATIC_URL1}/global/images/color_data/interpreta_title.png?{STATIC_CHANGE_TIME}" alt="数据解读">
                <p></p>
            </div>
            <!-- 推荐 -->
            <div class="section-chart-recommend js-section-recommend-analysis">
                <div class="h-line"></div>
                <div class="recommend-header">
                    <div class="title fl">推荐款式图</div>
                    <a class="more fr js-more-analysis" target="_blank" href="javascript:void(0);">
                        <span>查看更多</span>
                        <i></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="recommend-content">
                    <ul class="recommend-list clearfix">
                        <li>
                            <ul class="recommend-item clearfix js-recommend-item"></ul>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="pager js-recommend-pager">
                        <i class="l disabled"></i>
                        <i class="r"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- 色彩走势 -->
        <div class="section w1500 trend-color js-trend loading">
            <!-- 头部 -->
            <div class="section-header">
                <div class="fl title">色彩走势</div>
                <div class="info">统计最近3季色彩变化走势图，可以清晰知道每个颜色的走势情况，通过点击每个色系可查看该色系内所有颜色详情</div>
                <div class="fr">
                    <ul class="season clearfix js-trend-season">
                        <li class="active">早春</li>
                        <li>春夏</li>
                        <li>早秋</li>
                        <li>秋冬</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- 图表 -->
            <div class="section-chart">
                <div class="crumbs">
                    <div class="light-tips">
                        <i class="light"></i>
                        <div class="light-tips-content">
                            <i class="arrow"></i>
                            <ul>
                                <li>色彩走势是统计所有色系在最近3个季度内走势情况；</li>
                                <li>点击每个色系可以详细查看该颜色的详细情况。</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="crumbs-content js-crumbs-trend">
                        <div><span>色彩走势</span></div>
                        <div><i></i><span>一级色走势</span></div>
